metadata.name: NOUN 189 by Pixelord 1
metadata.description: Renowned digital artist Pixelord has unveiled a breathtaking reimagination of GnarsDAO's beloved mascot, Noun 189. This captivating collaboration brings together Pixelord's distinct artistic vision and GnarsDAO's pioneering spirit in the world of extreme sports and subDAOs.  Pixelord, known for pushing the boundaries of visual expression, has skillfully infused noun 189 with a vibrant energy that transcends traditional artwork. Through a masterful combination of bold colors, intricate details, and dynamic elements, Pixelord has breathed new life into GnarsDAO's iconic character
